<p><strong>SCP-CN-1439 戏班</strong></p>
<p><strong>作者：</strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/h-storm-z" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4761754); return false;"><img class="small" src="https://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4761754&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610107956" alt="H-Storm Z" style="background-image:url(https://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4761754)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/h-storm-z" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4761754); return false;">H-Storm Z</a></span></p>
<p><strong>人事页：</strong> <a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/hsz-file">http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/hsz-file</a></p>
<div class="credit-back" style="text-align: center;">
<p><iframe src="https://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--code/info%3Astyle/2" align="" frameborder="" height="" scrolling="no" width="" class="" style="height:2em;width: 100%;margin: 0;padding: 0;border: 0;background: transparent;"></iframe></p>
